 the lounge that started it all.\nPerfect for bespoke parties of up to 130 guests.\nContact Us\nThings to know\nAll checks have an automatic gratuity of 20% applied for the hardworking staff\nJojo’s reserves the right to enforce a 2-drink maximum at any time to allow us to service our many guests on time and keep people reasonably safe from over imbibing\nThere is no “cover charge”\nThe last seating is at 10:30 PM every Tuesday and Wednesday night.\nThe last seating is at 11:30 PM every Thursday, Friday, and Saturday night.",
